                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.95
              },
              "free_text": [
                " An active target, Cs2LiYCl6 (CLYC)",
                "scintillator."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two data sets were collected: one at a short",
                "flight path length 4.4 m and one at a long flight",
                "path length 9.4 m. Cross sections were obtained via",
                "ratio with the 6Li(n,alpha) 3H reaction using an",
                "active target experiment."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "For both data sets the 35Cl(n,p0 ) 35S cross section",
                "was determined relative to the 6Li(n,alpha) 3H",
                "reaction via sigma Cl(E) =",
                " (Ratm(6Li)*NCl(E)*sigma Li(E))/(Ratm(35Cl)*NLi(e)),",
                "where NCl and NLi are the numbers of observed",
                "35Cl(n,p0) and 6Li(n,alpha)3H reactions for a given",
                "incident neutron energy. Ratm(6Li) and Ratm(35Cl) are",
                "the numbers of 6Li and 35Cl atoms per CLYC molecule,",
                "respectively. 6Li(n,alpha) 3H cross section were taken",
                "from the upcoming ENDF/B-VIII.1 evaluation."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The uncertainty was determined via the",
                "standard deviation of the above distribution plus the",
                "quadrature added uncertainties from the Li and Cl",
                "abundances. Propagation of these uncertainties was",
                "performed via Monte Carlo."
              ]
            }
          ],
